{"tid":2415061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天下圍中｜G7領袖同意集體應對非市場導向政策行為 透過G20與中國交往","createTime":"2021-02-20T03:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T03:14:05.000Z","uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"63a240008b996444838820c307280f73c532541c","tid":2415061,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:05:48.000Z","msg":"七大工業國組織(G7)領袖周五舉行視像會議，同意集體應對「非市場導向」政策和行為，包括透過「二十國集團」(G20)與中國交往。美國總統拜登在會上稱，七大工業國必須反擊中國濫用經濟制度的行為。<br />\n<br />\nG7會後的聲明說：「為了支持一個對所有人平等互利的全球經濟系統，我們將與其他組織交往，特別是包括中國等大型經濟體的二十國集團組織。」<br />\n<br />\n聲明又說：「作為領袖，我們將互相集體磋商應對非市場導向政策和行為，並在應對影響所有國家的全球重要議題上互相合作。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210220/M62XHOQQOFA67FB72CFF7ED2XE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210220%2FM62XHOQQOFA67FB72CFF7ED2XE%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=362a7be5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210220%2FM62XHOQQOFA67FB72CFF7ED2XE%2F&h=ac4d7775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210220/M62XHOQQOFA67FB72CFF7ED2XE/</a>"},{"pid":"643a62a2606692d5f17aefdc9a37ff7dfa4105ed","tid":2415061,"uid":239336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qrFYdwM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqrFYdwM.gif&h=b35f82f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fd2d9722c283d45409f043b40c6667829d44dd7","tid":2415061,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f59b3234747b89a6bc5d8bd8813357747023939","tid":2415061,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"643a62a2606692d5f17aefdc9a37ff7dfa4105ed","tid":2415061,"uid":239336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qrFYdwM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqrFYdwM.gif&h=b35f82f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}